00:16:44.157 --> 00:16:44.740
SPEAKER 2: OK.

00:16:44.740 --> 00:16:47.360
So you seem to have pivoted
a lot, successfully,

00:16:47.360 --> 00:16:48.100
in your career.

00:16:48.100 --> 00:16:49.490
So how are you able to do it?

00:16:49.490 --> 00:16:52.700
What sort of challenges
did you face?

00:16:52.700 --> 00:16:56.280
DAVID DUCHOVNY: Oh,
well, I mean, it--

00:16:56.280 --> 00:16:59.070
I just think it's not that
I get bored so easily.

00:16:59.070 --> 00:17:02.960
I just think I have looked
for other modes of expression

00:17:02.960 --> 00:17:08.119
to convey whatever it is I
feel I was put here to convey,

00:17:08.119 --> 00:17:11.690
so just finding different
ways of expressing whatever

00:17:11.690 --> 00:17:14.000
it is on my mind or
my heart at the time.

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:18.740
So I started out as a
writer, unpublished,

00:17:18.740 --> 00:17:20.720
and then I became an actor.

00:17:20.720 --> 00:17:23.540
And then I went back to
being a writer, actor,

00:17:23.540 --> 00:17:27.050
and then I discovered music
and started writing, you know,

00:17:27.050 --> 00:17:31.280
lyrically that way and also
rediscovered myself as a prose

00:17:31.280 --> 00:17:32.280
writer at the same time.

00:17:32.280 --> 00:17:33.780
So I don't know.

00:17:33.780 --> 00:17:35.490
It wasn't really intentional.

00:17:35.490 --> 00:17:38.870
It's more just,
like, I don't know

00:17:38.870 --> 00:17:41.940
how to phrase it in a way
that makes total sense.

00:17:41.940 --> 00:17:47.420
But it's just like looking for
another window out or window

00:17:47.420 --> 00:17:51.650
open to communicate something
through that open window.

00:17:51.650 --> 00:17:54.240
I've lost it now.

00:17:54.240 --> 00:17:58.070
But I think-- but
your question, you

00:17:58.070 --> 00:17:59.820
know, it afforded me
a lot of opportunity.

00:17:59.820 --> 00:18:02.360
Because I had notoriety
as an actor to be given

00:18:02.360 --> 00:18:08.150
a listen as a musician
or a read as a novelist.

00:18:08.150 --> 00:18:09.800
At the same time,
though, you know,

00:18:09.800 --> 00:18:12.860
I'm open to attacks of
just being a dilettante.

00:18:12.860 --> 00:18:16.300
So it's both.

00:18:16.300 --> 00:18:19.340
I get an opportunity to reach
more people than I probably

00:18:19.340 --> 00:18:21.440
would if I didn't have
any kind of notoriety.

00:18:21.440 --> 00:18:23.504
But also I don't
get taken seriously.

00:18:23.504 --> 00:18:24.920
Like, what the
fuck are you doing?

00:18:24.920 --> 00:18:25.420
You know?

00:18:25.420 --> 00:18:27.960
Why don't you just
stay in your own lane?

00:18:27.960 --> 00:18:31.820
