00:18:33.320 --> 00:18:34.700
It was.

00:18:34.700 --> 00:18:37.280
When I used to actually
involve myself in it.

00:18:37.280 --> 00:18:39.840
SPEAKER 2: Yeah, when I first
followed you it was dilletante.

00:18:39.840 --> 00:18:41.160
I really like that tagline.

00:18:41.160 --> 00:18:42.626
DAVID DUCHOVNY:
I'll bring it back.

00:18:42.626 --> 00:18:43.360
Brad?

00:18:43.360 --> 00:18:43.860
Dilletante.

00:18:43.860 --> 00:18:45.950
[LAUGHTER]

00:18:45.950 --> 00:18:50.047
SPEAKER 2: Yeah, so
I guess my second--

00:18:50.047 --> 00:18:52.130
I think, from a lot of
your writing-- like I said,

00:18:52.130 --> 00:18:53.740
I read "Bucky Fucking Dent."

00:18:53.740 --> 00:18:54.746
I really enjoyed it.

00:18:54.746 --> 00:18:56.370
You can talk more
