AUDIENCE: [INAUDIBLE]?

00:39:25.590 --> 00:39:26.980
DAVID DUCHOVNY: Why male models?

00:39:26.980 --> 00:39:29.350
SPEAKER 2: David, do you
and your band have a--

00:39:29.350 --> 00:39:31.457
DAVID DUCHOVNY: I don't
