00:39:31.457 --> 00:39:32.800
[LAUGHTER]

00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:35.550
I can't remember which was
the hand that I modeled.

00:39:35.550 --> 00:39:37.670
SPEAKER 2: Oh, yeah.

00:39:37.670 --> 00:39:39.086
DAVID DUCHOVNY:
Left [INAUDIBLE]..

00:39:39.086 --> 00:39:40.520
